{
  "chapter": 204,
  "chapter_summary": "荣凤祥于洛阳举办五十寿宴，广邀各方豪杰。尚秀芳献艺贺寿，其风韵令在场美女黯然失色。席间玲珑娇与徐子陵交谈，尚秀芳主动邀约寇仲明日前往曼清院。独孤峰奉皇泰主杨侗钦命赐赠玉树，逼迫王世充当众跪接，意在挫折其士气。王薄主动挑战尉迟敬德，尉迟敬德以归藏鞭迎战，鞭法出神入化，竟能以鞭作棍令王薄措手不及。王薄亮出成名兵器定世鞭，两人激战数招，尉迟敬德虽功力稍逊却勇猛异常，最终两鞭首次交锋，胜负未分。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_rong_feng_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "荣凤祥",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "今天是荣某人五十贱降的日子，难得各位贵宾大驾光临，其中更不乏远自千里而来的好友，令荣某人备受荣宠，谨借一杯水酒，聊表敬谢各位的心意。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 204,
      "line_start": 19,
      "line_end": 21
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rong_feng_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "荣凤祥",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在菜肴上桌前，荣某人先送给各位贵宾一点惊喜，有请尚秀芳小姐。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 204,
      "line_start": 27,
      "line_end": 29
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rong_feng_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "荣凤祥",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "寇兄弟给老夫好好招呼芳小姐。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 204,
      "line_start": 53,
      "line_end": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_long_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "玲珑娇",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "你刚才为何对尚秀芳的演唱漫不经心呢？是嫌她唱得不好，还是不爱好乐曲？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 204,
      "line_start": 73,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_ling_long_jiao",
      "text": "我只是比较爱听情调幽怨的调子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 204,
      "line_start": 77,
      "line_end": 79
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_long_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "玲珑娇",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "昆仑山南月欲斜，牧人向月吹胡茄。胡茄羌笛，声最悲切，有机会公子定要一听。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 204,
      "line_start": 83,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_xiu_fang",
      "speaker_name": "尚秀芳",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "妾身住在曼清院，假若明天有空，可否找点时间来见见妾身呢？后天秀芳便要到关中去了！",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 204,
      "line_start": 87,
      "line_end": 89
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gu_feng",
      "speaker_name": "独孤峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "独孤峰奉皇泰主钦命，特来为荣老板贺寿，并代皇泰主赐赠玉树。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 204,
      "line_start": 99,
      "line_end": 101
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gu_feng",
      "speaker_name": "独孤峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "诸位平身！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 204,
      "line_start": 121,
      "line_end": 121
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rong_feng_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "荣凤祥",
      "listener": "char_du_gu_feng",
      "text": "独孤大人务要留下喝杯水酒。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 204,
      "line_start": 129,
      "line_end": 129
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gu_feng",
      "speaker_name": "独孤峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小弟有皇命在身，不宜久留，各位请了！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 204,
      "line_start": 131,
      "line_end": 133
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_bo",
      "speaker_name": "王薄",
      "listener": "char_li_shi_min",
      "text": "贵属尉迟仁兄不是想和老夫玩两手吗？何不趁此机会让老夫领教一下。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 204,
      "line_start": 137,
      "line_end": 139
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_chi_jing_de",
      "speaker_name": "尉迟敬德",
      "listener": "char_wang_bo",
      "text": "王公请不吝指点后学！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 204,
      "line_start": 145,
      "line_end": 147
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_bo",
      "speaker_name": "王薄",
      "listener": "char_yu_chi_jing_de",
      "text": "今天乃荣兄人喜的日子，所以我们的比试只是助兴性质，点倒即止，尉迟仁兄以为如何？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 204,
      "line_start": 153,
      "line_end": 155
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_chi_jing_de",
      "speaker_name": "尉迟敬德",
      "listener": "char_wang_bo",
      "text": "请前辈手下留情。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 204,
      "line_start": 159,
      "line_end": 159
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_chi_jing_de",
      "speaker_name": "尉迟敬德",
      "listener": "char_wang_bo",
      "text": "得罪了！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 204,
      "line_start": 169,
      "line_end": 171
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_bo",
      "speaker_name": "王薄",
      "listener": "char_yu_chi_jing_de",
      "text": "此鞭何名？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 204,
      "line_start": 175,
      "line_end": 175
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_chi_jing_de",
      "speaker_name": "尉迟敬德",
      "listener": "char_wang_bo",
      "text": "此鞭名归藏，长两丈三尺，前辈请不吝赐教。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 204,
      "line_start": 177,
      "line_end": 179
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_bo",
      "speaker_name": "王薄",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好鞭！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 204,
      "line_start": 185,
      "line_end": 185
    }
  ],
